archimate:BusinessObject.name: PreambleMarkingDetails
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
This class implements the semantics of the MarksPreambleWithConditioningResult association. The purpose of this class is to enable application- and vendor-specific implementations of preamble marking to be more easily modeled in DEN-ng.
Further details of this class will be provided in the next release of DEN-ng. This association defines which type of TrafficConditioningServices are used to mark the preamble of a packet with. The semantics of this association are defined by the PreambleMarkingDetails association class.
